<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>Architectural Design</h3>
<p>Creative and practical building designs for every lifestyle.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Interior Design</h3>
<p>Elegant interiors focused on comfort and functionality.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Farmhouse Planning</h3>
<p>Nature-inspired spaces with sustainable architecture.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Project Management</h3>
<p>End-to-end execution from concept to completion.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="projects">

<h2>Featured Projects</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
